{
  "stem": "365.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You had to clean it out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You cleaned as much as you could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And you had to stand in front of him, lift up your coat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he would tap it with his whip.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And of course, always a speck of dust came out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You received 25 lashes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So any new prisoner who came into that camp had to go through that, to receive his 25 lashes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "At one time when they were lashing a person and he was jumping extremely, couldn't hold on to the stool where he was bent over-- he couldn't hold on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So he went over to the couple that was holding him down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He says, step aside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I'll hold him down without any effort.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He pulled out his stiletto and put it to his neck.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He says, now jump.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "If he jumps, he's dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So that's how he got the lashes without jumping.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I received my first 25 lashes without a peep-- I could hardly walk away, of course.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With a bull whip or a horse whip.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a whip about three feet long--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--from leather.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not strip, just bent over a stool and lash you in the back, on your buttocks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not on the bare, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With your pants on, but the pants were a thin cotton.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you felt every stroke.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are black and blue after them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes you had even the skin cut through your clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Skin would be cut, and you are bleeding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On another occasion, it was already the end of '42, that one night we worked still at the construction site, dismantling everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we used to bring home, back to the barracks, roots-- old roots from trees that were dug up to use, because in the barrack was a cast-iron stove, like wood-burning stove.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
